    "Shortness of breath, Rhinorrhea, Gastrointestinal symptoms, Chest pain/tightness, Abdominal pain, Muscle pain, Loss of appetite, PaO2, SaO, Loss of smell, Heart rate, Systolic pressure, Diastolic pressure, Fatigue, Septic shock, Sore throat, pH, Temperature, Pharyngeal pain.",
    "The data is taken from the Bulgarian hospital St. George, then they are adapted in a case-based format that is suitable for the platform Colibri.The proposed case-based knowledge data model is compatible with CBROnto.",
